@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #121212
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #E6F0FF
  LifeLineBorderColor #E6F0FF
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #1C1C1C
  ParticipantBorderColor #E6F0FF
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #003366
  ParticipantFontColor #E6F0FF
  ActorBorderColor #E6F0FF
  ActorBackgroundColor #1C1C1C
  ActorFontColor #E6F0FF
  BoxBorderColor #E6F0FF
  BoxBackgroundColor #0F0F0F
  NoteBorderColor #E6F0FF
  NoteBackgroundColor #0F0F0F
  NoteFontColor #E6F0FF
}

title 架构时序图：关键调用链与数据流向（Host↔Simulator）

actor User as 用户
box "Host App (Electron)" #0F0F0F
  participant Renderer as 渲染进程\nhost-app/renderer.js
  participant Preload as 预加载桥\nhost-app/preload.js
  participant Main as 主进程\nhost-app/main.js
end box
box "Slave Simulator (Python)" #0F0F0F
  participant TCP as TCP服务端\nslave-sim/simulator.py
  participant Engine as 渲染引擎\nslave-sim/render_engine.py
  participant UDP as UDP推流\nslave-sim/simulator.py
end box

== 建立连接与遥测 ==
用户 -> Renderer : 点击“连接”
Renderer -> Preload : window.api.connect()
Preload -> Main : ipcRenderer.invoke('connect')
Main -> TCP : TCP connect(127.0.0.1:8888)
TCP --> Main : Accept + 进入 handle_client()
note over Main,TCP
真实实现：host-app/main.js 的 connect()/data 解析\nslave-sim/simulator.py 的 asyncio.start_server/handle_client
end note

loop 5Hz 遥测
  TCP -> TCP : send_telemetry()\nProtocol.pack(0x80, state)
  TCP --> Main : TCP data(cmdId=0x80, payload=state)
  Main -> Renderer : webContents.send('telemetry-data', payload)
end

alt CRC32 校验失败（异常分支）
  Main -> Main : 丢弃当前包并等待下一帧\n(解包时 CRC32 校验不通过)
end

== 视频链路（UDP）==
用户 -> Renderer : 点击“打开视频”
Renderer -> Preload : window.api.videoControl(true)
Preload -> Main : ipcRenderer.invoke('video-control', true)
Main -> TCP : sendPacket(0x10, {enabled:true})
TCP -> TCP : process_command(0x10)\nstate.video_enabled = True

loop ~30fps（asyncio.sleep(0.033)）
  Engine -> Engine : render()\nglReadPixels(640x480)\n-> BGR
  UDP -> UDP : Letterbox(640x480->320x240)\n+ OSD + JPEG(Q=70)
  alt 单帧过大（异常分支）
    UDP -> UDP : drop frame if len(data) >= 60000
  else 正常推流
    UDP --> Main : UDP sendto(jpeg_bytes, 8889)
    Main -> Renderer : webContents.send('video-frame', base64)
    Renderer -> Renderer : <img>.src = data:image/jpeg;base64,...
  end
end

== 场景切换（真实照片/CG）==
用户 -> Renderer : 点击“真实照片”
Renderer -> Preload : window.api.toggleRealPhoto()
Preload -> Main : ipcRenderer.invoke('toggle-real-photo')
Main -> TCP : sendPacket(0x11, {})
TCP -> Engine : renderer.real_photo_mode = !real_photo_mode

alt 真实照片资源缺失（异常分支）
  Engine -> Engine : load_real_photo()\n生成占位图避免崩溃
end

note bottom
本图仅覆盖代码中已存在的链路：IPC → TCP 命令 → 渲染/视频管线 → UDP 推流 → IPC 回传。\n读者重点关注：双链路解耦（TCP 控制/遥测 vs UDP 视频）、包头/长度/CRC32 校验的错误隔离、以及 UDP 单帧大小阈值对稳定性的影响。
end note
@enduml

